      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "FLAMING RONDA (2) bolted in first-up at Geraldton as the $1.55 favourite before a 1.2L defeat last time out at Ascot when closing off strongly from midfield. Pike now hops on board third-up and she rates highly on her two efforts back. Can bounce back to winning ways. ROSENTREA (1) comes back in trip today despite a 0.4L defeat over the mile last start at Pinjarra. The form out of that race has been solid and Nottle knows the mare well. Can sit handy from the barrier and appears the main danger. SETAGAYA (8) comes back to 1300m today after storming home from the back of the pack at Ascot most recently. CJP remains in the saddle and she boasts a good record at this track. Expected to be in the finish again. SO MUCH SERENITY (9) can sit handy from the draw and will up front for a long way. O'SO DEMANDING (7) is not out of this.",
